Package: ExactVaRTest
Title: Exact Finite-Sample VaR Back-Testing
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Yujian", "Chen", , "yujian.chen@polytechnique.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides fast dynamic-programming algorithms to compute the
    exact finite-sample distribution and p-values of the Christoffersen
    (1998) Unconditional Coverage (UC), Independence (IND) and Conditional
    Coverage (CC) tests for Value-at-Risk models.
